entry.tran: 任劳任怨的；不发牢骚的；不抱怨的
entry.def: If you describe someone as uncomplaining, you approve of them because they do difficult or unpleasant things and do not complain about them.

example.ex: He was a cheerful and uncomplaining travel companion.
example.tran: 他是一个乐观开朗从不抱怨的旅伴。
